.SH DESCRIPTION
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
This module models the download of an online (github) repository to a temporary
directory where some of its contents are copied to a local stow package.
.SH "CONFIGURATION AND ENVIRONMENT"
.IX Header "CONFIGURATION AND ENVIRONMENT"
.SS Options
.IX Subsection "Options"
None.
.SS Properties/attributes
.IX Subsection "Properties/attributes"
\fIdownload_dir\fR
.IX Subsection "download_dir"
.PP
Temporary directory repo files are downloaded to.
.PP
Required. Read-only. Path::Tiny instance.
.PP
\fIname\fR
.IX Subsection "name"
.PP
Project name for repository. Required. Read-only. String.
.PP
\fIdescription\fR
.IX Subsection "description"
.PP
Human-readable description of repository.
.PP
Required. Read-only. String.
.PP
\fIdownload_url\fR
.IX Subsection "download_url"
.PP
URL for downloading of remote repository. Could be used for a \f(CW\*(C`git clone\*(C'\fR
command or could be the current/latest asset archive file.
.PP
Required. Read-only. URI instance.
.PP
\fIasset_type\fR
.IX Subsection "asset_type"
.PP
Asset release file type. This value determines the command used to extract the
contents of the release asset archive file.
.PP
Required if <obtain_method> is "download-release-asset", otherwise optional.
Read-only. String. Default: undef. Allowed value: 'targz'.
.PP
\fIobtain_method\fR
.IX Subsection "obtain_method"
.PP
Download method for repository.
.PP
Required. Read-only. String.
Allowed values: 'git\-clone\-repository', 'download\-release\-asset'.
.PP
\fIrelease_path_extraction_regex\fR
.IX Subsection "release_path_extraction_regex"
.PP
Regular expression for extracting the release path from a filepath.
.PP
Required if <obtain_method> is "download-release-asset", otherwise optional.
Read-only. String. Default: undef.
.PP
\fIfilepath_mappings\fR
.IX Subsection "filepath_mappings"
.PP
All mappings between downloaded repository files and stow package templates
directory files.
.PP
Required. Read-write. Array of
App::My::PandocUpdateTemplates::FilepathMapping instances.
.PP
\fIdelete_paths\fR
.IX Subsection "delete_paths"
.PP
Repository files and directories to delete immediately after downloading and,
if necessary, extracting.
.PP
Required. Read-write. Array of Path::Tiny instances.
.PP
\fIignore_files\fR
.IX Subsection "ignore_files"
.PP
Repository files to ignore.
.PP
Required. Read-write. Array of Path::Tiny instances.
.PP
\fIsubstitutions\fR
.IX Subsection "substitutions"
.PP
String substitutions for repository files.
.PP
Required. Read-only. Array of
App::My::PandocUpdateTemplates::Substitution instances.
.PP
\fIobtained_files\fR
.IX Subsection "obtained_files"
.PP
Files obtained from repository.
.PP
Optional, not expected to be provided at instantiation.
Read-only: file list created on first read. Array of Path::Tiny instances.
.PP
\fIupdated_files\fR
.IX Subsection "updated_files"
.PP
Subset of <obtained_files> that represent updated files, that is, files that
are new or changed since last update. Optional, not expected to be provided at
instantiation. Read-write. Array of
App::My::PandocUpdateTemplates::FilepathMapping instances. Default: [].
.SS "Configuration file"
.IX Subsection "Configuration file"
None used.
.SS "Environment variables"
.IX Subsection "Environment variables"
None used.
